# ============================================================================
# SUMMARY
# ============================================================================
# 
# Required for production:
# ✅ Google OAuth (with production redirect URIs)
# ✅ Supabase (separate production project recommended)
# ✅ Stripe (live mode keys)
# ✅ PEPPER_SECRET (secure random string, 32+ chars)
# ✅ CAPTCHA (Cloudflare Turnstile recommended)
# ✅ Rate Limiting (enabled by default)
# 
# Recommended for production:
# ⚠️ Discord Webhook (separate production channel)
# ⚠️ Amazon Associates (same tag as dev)
# ⚠️ Argon2id parameters (tuned for Vercel Free Plan)
# 
# Optional for specific features:
# ⚠️ Monero (separate production wallet recommended)
# 
# Not needed in Vercel (managed automatically):
# ❌ DATABASE_URL (Vercel Postgres provides this)
# ❌ REDIS_URL (optional — only with external Redis/Upstash; omit on Vercel if unused)
# ❌ POSTGRES_* (Docker only)
# ❌ NODE_ENV (Vercel sets this)
# 
# ============================================================================
